code: @Override public List<PGPPublicKey> getEncryptionKeys(Exchange exchange, List<String> useridParts) throws Exception {     return PGPDataFormatUtil.findPublicKeys(useridParts, true, pgpPublicKeyRing). }

@Override public PGPPublicKey getPublicKey(Exchange exchange, long keyId, List<String> userIdParts) throws Exception {     return PGPDataFormatUtil.getPublicKeyWithKeyIdAndUserID(keyId, userIdParts, pgpPublicKeyRing). }
